locality: Flora of South Africa. Western Cape, Hottentots Holland Nature Reserve, Landsroskop, at path southbound.
Flora of South Africa. Cape Province. Caledon Div.: Hottentots Holland Mtns, 1 km from Gordon's Bay on road to Betty's Bay, NNW facing slopes.

Cape Point, c 3 km before turnoff Circular Road, before rock ledge is crossing street on the right. Fine white sand, shallow; rock cover 10% vegetation cover 50% (20% of which are Restionaceae), height 30 cm. Upland mixed Fynbos.

Flora of the Republic of South Africa. Western Cape Province: Stellenbosch District. Valley between the Stellenboschberg range and the Jonkersberg range. Upper end of valley, west slope of Jonkersberg.
